Description: Port to SDL2
 Replace SDL1 rendering backend with SDL2: SDL_Window, SDL_Renderer,
 SDL_Texture. The 8-bit indexed surface (Video_Memory) is converted to
 32-bit via SDL_BlitSurface before uploading to a streaming texture.
 SDL_RenderSetLogicalSize(320,240) provides automatic letterboxing when
 the window is resized. Update build-dependencies accordingly.
